content.html: I understand that Kanye is struggling psychologically, but his actions now verge on abuse. He’s using the public & media to pressure KK to come back to him, & KK has been objectified to the point that she’s not even seen as person. Why is all the concern for him not her?
content.value:
I understand that Kanye is struggling psychologically, but his actions now verge on abuse.

He’s using the public & media to pressure KK to come back to him, & KK has been objectified to the point that she’s not even seen as person.

Why is all the concern for him not her?
